# Design System Reference

**ALWAYS reference `DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` in the project root for UI consistency.**

## Quick Reference

### Colors (Dark Theme)
- Background: `#09090b` (zinc-950)
- Card: `#0a0a0b`
- Border: `#27272a` (zinc-800)
- Text: `#fafafa` (foreground)
- Muted text: `#a1a1aa` (zinc-400)
- Primary: `#fafafa`

### Typography
- Font: Geist (sans), Geist Mono (code)
- Page titles: `text-2xl font-semibold`
- Section headers: `text-lg font-medium`
- Body: `text-sm` or `text-base`
- Muted: `text-muted-foreground`

### Spacing
- Card padding: `p-4` (16px) or `p-6` (24px)
- Section gaps: `gap-6` (24px)
- Small gaps: `gap-2` (8px) or `gap-3` (12px)

### Layout
- Sidebar: 240px wide
- Top bar: 56px height
- Content max-width: 1400px
- Cards: `rounded-lg border bg-card`

### Component Classes
```tsx
// Card
<div className="rounded-lg border bg-card p-4">

// Section header
<h2 className="text-lg font-medium">

// Muted subtext
<p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground">

// Summary metric
<span className="text-3xl font-bold">
```

### Status Badge Colors
- New: `bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-500`
- Qualified: `bg-green-500/10 text-green-500`
- Proposal: `bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-500`
- Won: `bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500`
- Lost: `bg-red-500/10 text-red-500`

### Icons
Use Lucide React. Default size: 16-20px.
